**10³³ derivation** (from our scale verification):

```
λ = DM_halo_radius / Bohr_radius
  = 300 kpc / 5.3×10^{-11} m
```

**DM halo**: 300 kpc = 9.2×10^{21} m  
**Bohr radius**: 5.29×10^{-11} m  
```
λ = 9.2×10^{21} / 5.29×10^{-11} ≈ 1.74×10^{32} ≈ 10^{33} ✓
```

